full_text: Screened by NARA, 9/21/2023 UNITED STATES DEPARTMENT OF JUSTICE Immigration and Naturalization Service P.O. Box 1780 Calexico, California 92231 REFER TO THIS FILE NUMBER March 3, 1969 A17 984 698 (RHD/ICR) Mr. Ramon Fong Song Wong Morelos #251 Mexicali, B. C. , Mexico Dear Mr. Wong: Please come to the office shown below at the time and place indicated in connection with an official matter. OFFICE LOCATION Calexico, California Room No. Floor No. Main Floor DATE AND HOUR Tuesday through Friday from 8:30 a.m. to 4:30 p.m. ASK FOR REASON FOR APPOINTMENT An Immigration matter BRING WITH YOU This letter It is important that you keep this appointment and bring this letter with you. If you are unable to do so, notify this office at once, using the reverse side of this letter, and we will make another appointment for you. Very truly yours, Eldon W. Woolley Officer in Charge DINNEC TOR cc: George S. Lee, Esquire, 700 East Ninth Street, Los Angeles, California 90021 to ,d Form G-56 (Rev. 11-24-67) H
